OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying
OL,6,Fsunny and hot into this evening with
OL,7,Ftemperatures only slowly falling away
OL,8,Fafter dark. Clear skies continuing
OL,9,Fovernight and staying rather warm,
OL,10,Fmaking it quite uncomfortable for
OL,11,Fsleeping.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FAfter a warm start,
OL,14,Ftemperatures rapidly rising in the
OL,15,Fstrong sunshine and becoming
OL,16,Fexceptionally hot by the afternoon.
OL,17,FVery localised thunderstorms may
OL,18,Fdevelop later but most places will
OL,19,Fstay dry.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
